Package org.kawanfw.file.api.filters

Provides simple built-in FileFilter and FilenameFilter for usage on client or server side.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FileFilterDirsOnly
    A FileFilter that accepts only files that are directory.
    FileFilterFilesOnly
    A FileFilter that accepts only files that are not a directory.
    FilenameFilterDirsOnly
    A FilenameFilter that accepts only files that are directory.
    FilenameFilterFilesOnly
    A FilenameFilter that accepts only files that are not directory.
    RemoteFileFilter
    A FileFilter that extends this class is supposed to already exist on the remote server.
    RemoteFilenameFilter
    A FilenameFilter that extends this class is supposed to already exist on the remote server.
